7 An Act relating to children; amending 10A O.S. 2021,
Section 1-9-107, which relates to the Successful
8 Adulthood Act; providing documents certain children
leaving foster care shall be provided; providing that
9 certain documents be given to individuals being
released from the custody of the Office of Juvenile
10 Affairs; providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.
